Diane Craig https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diane_Craig 0 Diane Mary Craig (born 9 June 1949) is an actress born in County Down, Northern Ireland but who is best known for her performances on Australian television. She is married to Australian actor and comedian Garry McDonald.
